hadiths[57]{hadithnumber,text}:
6861,aik sahib yani khud aap ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! Allah ke nazdeek kon sa gunah sabse bada hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye ke tum Allah ka kisi ko Sharik thehrao jabke us ne tumhen paida kya hai. puchha : phir kon sa ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir ye ke tum apne ladkey ko us dar se mar dalo ke wo tumharey sath khana khaaeyga. puchha : phir kon sa? farmaya phir ye ke tum apne padosi ki biwi se zina karo. phir Allah Taala ne uski tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil ki والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر wla يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق wla يزنون ومن يفعل ذلك يلق أثاما يضاعف له العذاب''aur wo log jo Allah ke sath kisi doosrey maabood ko nahi pukaartey aur na kisi aisey insan ki nahaq jaan letey hain jisey Allah ne haram kya aur na zina kartey hain aur jo koi aisa karega .'' aakhir aayat tak.
6862,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''momin us waqt tak apne Deen ke barey mein barabar kushaada rehta hai) usey har waqt maghfirat ki ummeed rehti hai) jab tak nahaq khoon na karey jahan nahaq kya to maghfirat ka darwaza tang ho jata hai.''
6863,"halaakat ka bhanwar jis mein girney ke baad phir nikalney ki ummeed nahi hai wo nahaq khoon karna hai, jis ko Allah Taala ne haram kya hai."
6864,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse pahley (qiyamat ke din) logon ke darmyan khoon kharaabey ke faisley kiye jaengey. ''
6865,"wo badr ki ladai main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sharik they ke aap ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! agar jang ke doran meri kisi kaafir se mudbhed ho jaey aur ham aik doosrey ko qatl karne ki koshish karne lagein phir wo mere hath par apni talwaar mar kar usey kaat de aur uske baad kisi darakht ki aad lekar kahey ke main Allah par eman laya to kya main usey uske us iqrar ke baad qatl kar sakta hoon? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey qatl na karna. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! us ne to mera hath bhi kaat daala aur ye iqrar us waqt kya jab usey yaqin ho gaya ke ab main usey qatl hi kar doonga? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey qatl na karna kyonke agar tum ne usey Islam laney ke baad qatl kar diya to wo tumharey martabe mein hoga jo tumhara usey qatl karne se pahley tha yani ma'soom, aur tum uske martabe mein hogey jo uska us kalima ke iqrar se pahley tha jo usney ab kya hai (yani zaalim)."
6866,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya tha ke agar koi musalman kaafiron ke sath rehta ho phir wo dar ke maarey apna eman chhipata ho, agar wo apna eman zahir kar de aur to usko mar daley ye kyon kar durust hoga khud tum bhi to Makka mein pahley apna eman chhipaatey they."
6867,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo jaan nahaq qatl ki jaey iske ( gunah ka ( aik hissey Adam (Alaihissalam) ke pahley betey (Qaabeel par) padta hai.''
6868,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere baad kaafir na bin jana ke tum mein se kuchh kuchh ki gardan maarney lag jaao.''
6869,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke din farmaya '' logon ko khamosh kara do, ( phir farmaya ( tum mere baad kaafir na bin jana ke tum mein se koi kisii ki gardan maarney lagey.'' us hadis ki riwayat Abu-Bakar aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ki hai."
6870,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' kabeera gunah Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik thehrana , waalidain ki nafarmani karna ya farmaya ke nahaq doosrey ka maal leney ke liye jhooti qism khana hain.'' shak Shoba ko tha aur Muaz ne bayan kya, unse Shoba ne bayan kya, kaha kabeera gunah Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik thehrana , kisi ka maal nahaq leney ke liye jhooti qism khana aur waalidain ki nafarmani karna ya kaha ke kisi ki jaan lenaa."
6871,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' gunah kabeera '' aur ham se Amr ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Abu-Bakar ne aur unse Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse badey gunah Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik thehrana , kisi ki nahaq jaan lena , waalidain ki nafarmani karna aur jhoot bolnaa hain ya farmaya ke jhooti gawahi dena."
6872,hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila juhaina ki aik shaakh ki taraf ( muhim par) bhejaa. bayan kya ke phir ham ne un logon ko subah ke waqt ja liya aur unhein shikast de di. rawi ne bayan kya ke main aur qabila Ansar ke aik sahib qabila juhaina ke aik shakhs tak pahunchey aur jab ham ne usey gher liya to usne kaha ( لا إله إلا الله ( Ansari sahabi ne to (ye suntey hi ( hath rok liya lekin maine apne neze se usey qatl kar diya. rawi ne bayan kya ke jab ham wapas aaey to is waaqie ki khabar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mili . bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya '' Usama ! kya tum ne kalima ( لا إله إلا الله (ka iqrar karne ke baad usey qatl kar dala. '' maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! us ne sirf jaan bachaney ke liye iska iqrar kya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ''tum ne usey ( لا إله إلا الله (ka iqrar karne ke baad qatl kar dala. '' bayan kya ke Nabi Karim us jumla ko itni baar dohraatey rahe ke mere dil mein ye khahish paida ho gaee ke kash! main is se pahley musalman na hua hota.
6873,"main un naqeebon mein se tha jinhoney ( Mina mein Lailatal-Aqbaa ke mauqe par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi. ham ne iski bait (ahad ( ki thi ke ham Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thahraaeingey, ham chori nahi karengey, zina nahi karengey, kisi ki nahaq jaan nahi lengey jo Allah ne haram ki hai, ham loot-maar nahi karengey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nafarmani nahi karengey aur ye ke agar ham ne is par amal kya to hamein jannat milegii aur agar ham ne unmein se kisi tarah ka gunah kya to uska faisla Allah tabarak w taala ke yahan hoga."
6874,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne ham par hathiyar uthaya wo ham mein se nahi hai.''abu-Moosa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis riwayat ki hai.
6875,"main un sahib ( Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu)) ki jange-jamal mein madad ke liye taiyaar tha ke Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se meri mulaqat hui. unhon-ne poochha, kahan ka irada hai? maine kaha ke un sahib ki madad ke liye jana chahta hun. unhon-ne farmaya ke wapas chaley jao maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke jab 2 musalman talwaar kheench kar aik doosrey se bhid jayen to qaatil aur maqtool donon dozakh mein jatey hain. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aik to qaatil tha lekin maqtool ko saza kyon milegii ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo bhi apne qaatil ke qatl par aamada tha."
6876,"aik Yahudi ne aik ladki ka sar 2 pattharon ke darmyan rakh kar kuchal diya phir us ladki se puchha gaya ke ye kis ne kya hai? falan ne, falan ne? aakhir jab us Yahudi ka naam liya gaya (to ladki ne sar ke ishara se haan kaha ( phir Yahudi ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan laya gaya aur us se poochh gachh ki jati rahi yahan tak ke usne jurm ka iqrar kar liya chunanche uskaa sar bhi pattharon se kuchlaa gaya."
6877,"Madina Munawra mein aik ladki chandi ke zewar pahney bahar niklii. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir usey aik Yahudi ne patthar se mar diya. jab usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya gaya to abhi usmein jaan baqi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha tumhen falan ne maara hai? is par ladki ne apna sar ( inkar ke liye) uthaya , phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha tumhen falan ne maara hai? ladki ne is par bhi uthaya . teesri martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne poochha, falan ne tumhen maara hai? is par ladki ne apna sar nichey ki taraf jhukaa liya ( iqrar kartey huey jhukaa liya ( chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us shakhs ko bulaya tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 pattharon se kuchal kar usey qatl karaya."
6878,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi musalman ka khoon jo kalima la ilaaha-illallaah Muhammadur-rasoolullaah ka manney wala ho halal nahi hai albatta teen Suraton mein jaaiz hai. jaan ke badle jaan leney waalaa, shadi shuda ho kar zina karne wala aur Islam se nikal janey wala ( murtad ( jamat ko chhod dene wala. ''"
6879,"aik Yahudi ne aik ladki ko iske chandi ke zewar ke laalach mein mar daala tha. us ne ladki ko patthar se maara phir ladki Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laai gaee to uske jism mein jaan baqi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya tumhen falan ne maara hai? us ne sar ke ishara se inkar kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dobara poochha, kya tumhen falan ne maara hai? us martaba bhi us ne sar ke ishaarey se inkar kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab teesri martaba puchha to usne sar ke ishara se iqrar kya. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Yahudi ko 2 pattharon mein kuchal kar qatl kar diya."
6880,"qabila khuza'aa ke logon ne aik aadmi ko qatl kar diya tha aur Abdullah-bin -Rijaa ne kaha, unse Harab bin Shaddad ne, unse Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne, unse abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke fateh Makka ke mauqe par qabila khuza'aa ne bani Leis ke aik shakhs ko apne jahiliyat ke maqtool ke badle mein qatl kar diya tha. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur farmaya ''Allah taala ne Makka Mukarrama se haathiyon ke (shaah Yaman Abraha ke) lashkar ko rok diya tha lekin us ne apne rasool aur mominon ko is par ghalba diya. haan ye mujh se pahley kisi ke liye halal nahi hua tha aur na mere baad kisi ke liye halal hoga aur mere liye bhi din ko sirf ghadi bhar ke liye. ab is waqt se iski hurmat phir qaaim ho gaee. ( sun lo ( iska kaantaa na ukhaadaa jaey, iska darakht na taraashaa jaey aur siwa iske jo elaan karne ka irada rakhta hai koi bhi yahan ki giri hui cheez na uthaey aur dekho jiska koi azeez qatl kar diya jaey to usey 2 baton mein ikhtiyar hai ya usey uska khoon baha diya jaey ya qisaas diya jaey. ye waz (nasihat) sun kar is par aik yamnii sahib Abu-Shah naam ke khadey huey aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! is waz (nasihat) ko mere liye likhwaa dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye waz (nasihat) Abu-Shah ke liye likh do. iske baad Quraish ke aik sahib Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kaha : ya Rasulullah izkhir ghaas ki ijazat farma dijiye kyonke ham usey apne gharon main aur apni qabron mein bichhaatey hain. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne izkhir ghaas ukhaadney ki ijazat de di aur is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ubaidullah ne Sheban ke waaste se haathiyon ke waaqie ke zikr ke silsile mein ki. kuchh ne abu-Nueim ke hawale se ( القتل‏ . Mina (ka lafz riwayat ka hai aur Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke ya maqtool ke ghar walon ko qisaas diya jaey."
6881,"Bani-Israeel mein sirf qisaas ka riwaaj tha, diyat ki sura nahi thi. phir is ummat ke liye ye hukm nazil hua ( كتب عليكم القصاص في القتلى‏ ( الخ . Ibne-Abbas ne kaha ( فمن عفي له من أخيه شىء‏ ( se yahi murad hai ke maqtool ke waaris jan-boojhkar qatl karney mein diyat par razi ho jayen aur) فاتباع بالمعروف‏ ( se ye murad hai ke maqtool ke waaris dastoor ke muwafiq qaatil se diyat ka taqaza karein ( وآداء اليه باحسان ( se ye murad hai ke qaatil achi tarah khush dillii se diyat ada kare."
6882,"Allah Taala ke nazdeek logon ( musalmanon ( mein sabse zyada mabghooz (jinpar ghussa bhadakta hai) teen tarah ke log hain. haram mein zyadti karne waalaa, doosra jo Islam mein jahiliyat ki rasmon par chalney ka khaahishmand ho, teesrey wo shakhs jo kisi aadmi ka nahaq khoon karne ke liye iske peechhey lagey."
6883,"mushrekeen ne Uhud ki ladai mein pahley shikast khaaii thi (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha mujh se Muhammad-bin Harab ne bayan kya, unse Abu-Marwaan Yahya ibne-abi Zakariya ne bayan kya, unse Hisham ne, unse Urwa ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke iblees Uhud ki ladai mein logon mein cheekhaa . aey Allah ke bando! apne peechhey walon se, magar ye suntey hi aagey ke musalman peechhey ki taraf palat padey yahan tak ke musalmanon ne ( ghalati mein) Huzefa ke walid Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ko qatl kar diya. is par Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye mere walid hain, mere walid ! lekin unhein qatl hi kar dala. phir Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Allah tumhari maghfirat kare. bayan kya ke mushrekeen ki aik jamat maidan se bhag kar Taaif tak pahunch gaee thi."
6884,aik Yahudi ne aik ladki ka sar 2 pattharon ke darmyan mein lekar kuchal diya tha. us ladki se puchha gaya ke ye tumharey sath kis ne kiya? kya falan ne kya hai? kya falan ne kya hai? aakhir jab us Yahudi ka naam liya gaya to usne apne sar ke ishaarey se ( haan ( kaha phir Yahudi laya gaya aur us ne iqrar kar liya chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se iska bhi sar patthar se kuchal diya gaya. Hammam ne 2 pattharon ka zikr kya hai.
6885,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi ko aik ladki ke badle mein qatl kara diya tha, Yahudi ne us ladki ko chandi ke zewaraat ke laalach mein qatl kar diya tha."
6886,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh main ( maut ke marz ke mauqe par) aap ki marzii ke khilaf ham ne dawaa dali . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere halaq mein dawaa na dalo lekin ham ne samjha ke mareez honey ki wjah se dawaa peeney se nafrat kar rahe hain lekin jab aapko hosh hua to farmaya ke tum jitney log ghar mein ho sab ke halaq mein zabardastii dawaa dali jaey siwa Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke ke wo us waqt maujood nahi they.
6887,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham aakhiri ummat hain lekin (qiyamat ke din) sabse aagey rehney waley hain."
6888,(riwaayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( agar koi shakhs terey ghar main ( kisi suraakh ya jangley wghaira se) tum se ijazat liye baghair jhank raha ho aur tum usey kankari maaro jis se uski aankh phoot jaey to tum par koi saza nahi hai na gunah hoga na duniya ki koi saza laagu hogi.
6889,"aik sahib Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar mein jhank rahe they, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki taraf teer ka phal badhaya tha. maine puchha ke ye hadis tum se kis ne bayan ki hai? to unhon-ne bayan kya Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne."
6890,"Uhud ki ladai mein mushrekeen ko pahley shikast ho gaee thi lekin iblees ne chilla kar kaha aey Allah ke bando! peechhey ki taraf walon se bacho ! chunanche aagey ke log palat padey aur aagey waley peechhey walon se (jo musalman hi they) bhid gaey. achcha Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha to unke walid Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) they. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke bando! ye to mere walid hain, mere walid . bayan kya ke Allah ki qism musalman unhein qatl karke hi hatey . is par Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Allah tumhari maghfirat kare. Urwa ne bayan kya ke is waaqie ka sadma Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko aakhir waqt tak raha."
6891,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar ki taraf nikley. jamat ke aik sahib ne kaha aamir! hamein apni hadii (oont ko tez hankaaney ka geet) sunaaiye . unhon-ne hadi padhni shuru ki to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kon sahib ga ga kar oonton ko haank rahe hain? logon ne kaha ke Aamir hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah un par raham kare. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne hamein Aamir se fayda kyon nahi uthaney diya. chunanche Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) usi raat ko apni hi talwaar se Shahid ho gaey. logon ne kaha ke unke aamaal barbad ho gaey, unhon-ne khudkushii kar li (kyonke aik Yahudi par hamla kartey waqt khud apni talwaar se zakhmi ho gaey they) jab main wapas aaya aur maine dekha ke log aapas mein keh rahe hain ke Aamir ke aamaal barbad ho gaey to main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya : aey Allah ke Nabi ! aap par mere bap aur maan fidaa hon, ye log kehtey hain ke Aamir ke sarey aamaal barbad huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs ye kehta hai ghalat kehta hai. Aamir ko dohra ajr milega wo ( Allah ke raaste mein) mashaqqat uthaney waley aur jihad karne waley they aur kis qatl ka ajr us se badh kar hoga?"
6892,aik shakhs ne aik shakhs ke hath mein daant se kaataa to usne apna hath kaatney waley ke munh mein se kheench liya jis se uske aagey ke 2 daant toot gaey phir donon apna jhagdaa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apne hi bhai ko is tarah daant se kat-tey ho jaisey oont kaat'taa hai tumhen diyat nahi milegii.
6893,mein aik jang mein bahar tha aur aik shakhs ne daant se kaat liya tha jiski wjah se iske aagey ke daant toot gaey they phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us muqaddima ko baatil qarar de kar uski diyat nahi dilai .
6894,Nazar ki beti ne aik ladki ko tamaancha maara tha aur uske daant toot gaey they. log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas muqaddima laey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qisaas ka hukm diya.
6895,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ye aur ye barabar yani chhanguliyaa aur angoothaa diyat mein barabar hain.''
6896,"aik ladkey Aseel naam ke ko dhokey se qatl kar diya gaya tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke sarey ahal san'aa ( Yaman ke log ( iske qatl mein Sharik hotey to main sab ko qatl kara deta aur Mughira bin-Hakim ne apne walid se bayan kya ke char aadmiyon ne aik bachchey ko qatl kar diya tha to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye baat farmai thi Abu-Bakar , ibne-Zubair , Ali aur Suwed bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) ne chaantey ka badla dilwaayaa tha aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne durrey ki jo mar aik shakhs ko hui thi iska badla leney ke liye farmaya aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne teen kodon ka qisaas leney ka hukm diya aur Shureh ne kode aur kharaash lagaaney ki saza di thi."
6897,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke marz mein aap ke munh mein zabardastii dawaa dali . halanke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ishara kartey rahe ke dawaa na dali jaey lekin ham ne samjha ke mareez ko dawaa se jo nafrat hoti hai) uski wjah se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe hain) phir jab aapko fayda hua to farmaya, maine tumhen nahi kaha tha ke dawaa na dalo . bayan kya ke ham ne arz kya ke aap ne dawaa se na-gawari ki wjah se aisa kya hoga? is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se har aik ke munh mein dawaa dali jaey aur main dekhta rahunga siwaey Abbas ke kyonke wo us waqt wahan maujood hi na they."
6898,"unki qaum ke kuchh log khaibar gaey aur (apne apney kaamon ke liye) mukhtalif jaghon mein alag alag gaey phir apne mein ke aik shakhs ko maqtool paya. jinhein wo maqtool miley they, unse un logon ne kaha ke hamarey sathi ko tum ne qatl kya hai. unhon-ne kaha ke na ham ne qatl kya aur na hamein qaatil ka pata malum hai? phir ye log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaey aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! ham khaibar gaey aur phir ham ne wahan apne aik sathi ko maqtool paya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein jo bada hai wo baat kare. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qaatil ke khilaf gawahi laao. unhon-ne kaha ke hamarey paas koi gawahi nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir ye ( Yahudi ( qism khaaengey (aur unki qism par faisla hoga ( unhon-ne kaha ke yahudiyon ki qasmon ka koi eitibaar nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey pasand nahi farmaya ke maqtool ka khoon rayegaan jaey chunanche aap ne sadqe ke oonton mein se so oont ( khud hi ( diyat mein diye."
6899,"Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ne aik din darbar aam kya aur sab ko ijazat di. log dakhil huey to unhon-ne puchha : qasaama ke barey main tumhara kya khayal hai? kisi ne kaha ke qasaama ke zariey qisaas lena haq hai aur khulafaa ne iske zariey qisaas liya hai. is par unhon-ne mujh se puchha : abu-Qilaba ! tumhari kya raey hai? aur mujhey Awam ke sath la khada kar diya. maine arz kya : ya ameerul-momineen ! aap ke paas Arab ke sardaar aur sharif log rahtey hain aap ki kya raey hogi agar unmein se pachaas aadmi kisi Dimashqi ke shadi shuda shakhs ke barey mein zina ki gawahi dein jabke un logon ne us shakhs ko dekha bhi na ho kya aap unki gawahi par us shakhs ko rajm (sangsaar) kar dengey. ameerul-momineen ne farmaya ke nahi. phir maine kaha ke aap ka kya khayal hai agar unhein ( ashraaf arab) mein se pachaas afraad teiswin ke kisi shakhs ke mutaalliq chori ki gawahi de dein usko baghair dekhey to kya aap uska hath kaat dengey ? farmaya ke nahi. phir maine kaha, to Allah ki qism ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi kisi ko teen haalaton ke siwa qatl nahi karaya. aik wo shakhs jisne kisi ko zulm kartey huey qatl kya ho aur uske badley mein qatl kya gaya ho. doosra wo shakhs jisne shadi ke baad zina kya ho. tesraa wo shakhs jisne Allah aur uske rasool se jang ki ho aur Islam se phir gaya ho. logon ne is par kaha, kya Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis nahi bayan ki hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chori ke maamle mein hath pair kaat diye they aur aankhon mein silai phirwaaii thi aur phir unhein dhoop mein dalwaa diya tha. maine kaha ke main aap logon ko Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis sunata hun mujh se Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke qabila ukul ke aath (8) afraad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur aap se Islam par bait ki, phir Madina Munawra ki aab w hua unhein na-muwaafiq hui aur wo bimar pad gaey to unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uski shikayat ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke phir kyon nahi tum hamarey charwaahey ke sath iske oonton mein chaley jatey aur oonton ka doodh aur unka peshab peetey . unhon-ne arz kya kyon nahi. chunanche wo nikal gaey aur oonton ka doodh aur peshab piyaa aur sihat mand ho gaey. phir unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charwaahey ko qatl kar diya aur oont hankaa ley gaey. iski itlaa jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pahunchi to aap ne unki talash mein aadmi bhejey, phir wo pakdey gaey aur laey gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur unke bhi hath aur paon kaat diye gaey aur unki aankhon mein silai pher di gaee phir unhein dhoop mein dalwaa diya aur aakhir wo mar gaey. maine kaha ke unke amal se badh kar aur kya jurm ho sakta hai Islam se phir gaey aur qatl kya aur chori ki. Anba-bin-Saeed ne kaha maine aaj jaisi baat kabhi nahi suni thi. maine kaha : Anba! kya tum meri hadis radd kartey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi aap ne ye hadis waqia ke mutabiq bayan kar di hai. Allah ki qism ! ahal Sham (Syria) ke sath us waqt tak khair w bhalai rahegi jab tak ye Shekh ( abu-Qilaba ( unmein maujood raheingey. maine kaha ke us qasaama ke silsile main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik sunnat hai. Ansar ke kuchh log aap ke paas aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baat ki phir unmein se aik sahib unke samney hi nikley ( khaibar ke irada se) aur wahan qatl kar diye gaey. iske baad doosrey sahaba bhi gaey aur dekha ke unke sath khoon mein tadap rahe hain. un logon ne wapas aa kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski itlaa di aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! hamarey sath guftgu kar rahe they aur achcha wo hamein ( khaibar mein) khoon mein tadaptey miley. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nikley aur puchha ke tumhara kis par shuba hai ke unhon-ne unko qatl kya hai. sahaba ne kaha ke ham samajhtey hain ke yahudiyon ne hi qatl kya hai phir aap ne yahudiyon ko bula bheja aur unse puchha kya tum ne unhein qatl kya hai? unhon-ne inkar kar diya to aap ne farmaya, kya tum maan jaogey agar pachaas Yahudi iski qism lein ke unhon-ne maqtool ko qatl nahi kya hai. sahaba ne arz kya : ye log zara bhi parwah nahi karengey ke ham sab ko qatl karne ke baad phir qism kha lein (ke qatl unhon-ne nahi kya hai) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya to phir tum mein se pachaas aadmi qism kha lein aur khoon baha ke mustahiq ho jaaein. sahaba ne arz kya : ham bhi qism khaney ke liye taiyaar nahi hain. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein apne paas se khoon baha diya ( abu-Qilaba ne kaha ke) maine kaha ke zamane jahiliyat mein qabila huzail ke logon ne apne aik aadmi ko apne mein se nikal diya tha phir wo shakhs Batha mein Yaman ke aik shakhs ke ghar raat ko aaya. itney mein unmein se koi shakhs bedaar ho gaya aur us ne is par talwaar se hamla karke qatl kar diya. iske baad huzail ke log aaey aur unhon-ne yamnii ko) jisne qatl kya tha) pakda aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas le gaey Haj ke zamane mein aur kaha ke usne hamarey aadmi ko qatl kar diya hai. yamnii ne kaha ke unhon-ne usey apni braadrii se nikal diya tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ab huzail ke pachaas aadmi uski qism khaaein ke unhon-ne usey nikala nahi tha. bayan kya ke phir unmein se 49 aadmiyon ne qism khaaii phir unhein ke qabeele ka aik shakhs Sham (Syria) se aaya to unhon-ne us se bhi mutalba kya ke wo qism khaaey lekin us ne apni qism ke badle mein aik hazaar dirham de kar apna peechhaa qism se chhudaa liya. hazliyon ne uski jagah aik doosrey aadmi ko taiyaar kar liya phir wo maqtool ke bhai ke paas gaya aur apna hath iske hath se milaayaa. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir ham pachaas jinhoney qism khaaii thi rawaana huey. jab maqam nakhla par pahunchey to barish ne unhein aaya. sab log pahaad ke aik ghaar mein ghus gaey aur ghaar un pachaason ke uper gir padaa. jinhoney qism khaaii thi aur sab ke sab mar gaey. albatta donon hath milaaney waley bach gaey. lekin unke peechhey se aik patthar ludhak kar gira aur us se maqtool ke bhai ki taang toot gaee iske baad wo aik saal aur zinda raha phir mar gaya. maine kaha ke Abdul-Malik bin Marwan ne qasaama par aik shakhs se qisaas li thi phir usey apne kiye huey par nadaamat hui aur us ne un pachaason ke mutaalliq jinhoney qism khaaii thi hukm diya aur unke naam rajister se kaat diye gaey phir unhon-ne Sham (Syria) bhej diya."
6900,aik aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik hujre mein jhaankney laga to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) teer ka phal lekar uthey aur chahtey they ke ghafalat mein usko mar dein.
6901,aik aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darwaze ke aik suraakh se andar jhaankney laga. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas lohey ka kangha tha jis se aap sar jhaad rahe they. jab aap ne usey dekha to farmaya ke agar mujhey malum hota ke tum mera intizar kar rahe ho to main usey tumhari aankh mein chubho detaa. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (ghar ke andar aaney ka ( izn leney ka hukm diya gaya hai wo isi liye to hai ke nazar na padey.
6902,abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar koi shakhs tumhari ijazat ke baghair tumhen (jab ke tum ghar ke andar ho ( jhank kar dekhey aur tum usey kankari mar do jis se uski aankh phoot jaey to tum par koi gunah nahi hai.''
6903,"maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya aap ke paas koi aisi cheez bhi hai jo Quran Majeed mein nahi hai aur aik martaba unhon-ne is tarah bayan kya ke jo logon ke paas nahi hai. is par unhon-ne kaha ke us zaat ki qism jisne daney se kaunpal ko phaad kar nikala hai aur makhlooq ko paida kya. hamarey paas Quran Majeed ke siwa aur kuchh nahi hai. siwa us samajh ke jo kisi shakhs ko uski kitab mein di jaey aur jo kuchh us saheefe mein hai. maine puchha saheefe mein kya hai? farmaya khoon baha ( diyat ( se mutaalliq ehkaam aur qaidi ke chhudaaney ka hukm aur ye ke koi musalman kisi kaafir ke badle mein qatl nahi kya jaeyga"
6904,qabila huzail ki 2 aurton ne aik dusri ko (patthar se) maara jis se aik ke pet ka bachcha (janeen) gir gaya phir is ( silsile ( mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey aik ghulam ya kaneez dene ka faisla kya.
6905,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse aik aurat ke hamal gira dene ke khoon baha ke silsile mein mashwara kya to Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghulam ya kaneez ka is silsiley mein faisla kya tha.
6906,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska faisla kya tha to wo maujood they.
6907,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon se qism de kar puchha ke kis ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hamal girney ke silsiley mein faisla suna hai? Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, aap ne usmein aik ghulam ya kaneez dene ka faisla kya tha."
6908,is par apna koi gawah laao. chunanche Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye faisla kya tha.
6909,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bani Lahyaan ki aik aurat ke janeen (ke girney) par aik ghulam ya kaneez ka faisla kya tha. phir wo aurat jiske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne diyat dene ka faisla kya tha uska intiqal ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faisla kya ke uski meeraas uske ladkon aur uske shauhar ko milegii aur diyat iske dadhiyaal walon ko deeni hogi.
6910,banii-Huzail ki 2 auratein aapas mein ladiin aur aik ne dusri aurat par patthar phenk maara jis se wo aurat apne pet ke bachchey (janeen) samet mar gaee. phir ( maqtoola ke rishtedar ( muqaddima Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darbar mein ley gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faisla kya ke pet ke bachchey ka khoon baha aik ghulam ya kaneez deeni hogi aur aurat ke khoon baha ko qaatil aurat ke aaqila ( aurat ke bap ki taraf se rishtedar usba (ke zimma wajib qarar diya.
6911,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Talha (Raziallahu anhu) mera hath pakad kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laey aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! Anas samajh daar ladka hai aur ye aap ki khidmat karega . Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat safar mein bhi ki aur ghar par bhii. Allah ki qism ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi mujh se kisi cheez ke mutaalliq jo maine kar diya ho ye nahi farmaya ke ye kaam tum ne is tarah kyon kya aur na kisi aisi cheez ke mutaalliq jisey maine na kya ho aap ne ye nahi farmaya ke ye kaam tum ne is tarah kyon nahi kya.
6912,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''chaupaaey agar kisi ko zakhmi kar dein to unka khoon baha nahi, kuwein mein girney ka koi khoon baha nahi, kaan mein dabney ka koi khoon baha nahi aur dafeeney mein panchwan hissey hai.''"
6913,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''be-zabaan janwar kisi ko zakhmi karey to uski diyat kuchh nahi hai, isi tarah kaan mein kaam karne se koi nuqsan pahunchey, isi tarah kuwein mein kaam karne se aur jo kaafiron ka maal dafn kya hua miley usmein panchwan hissey sarkaar mein liya jaaeyga.''"
6914,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs aisi jaan ko mar daley jis se ahad kar chuka ho ( uski aman de chuka ho ( jaisey zimmii , kaafir ko to wo jannat ki khushbu bhi na soonghey ga (usmein dakhil hona to bahut door) halanke jannat ki khushbu chalis (40) baras ki raah se malum hoti hai.''"
6915,"maine abu-Juhaifa se suna, unhon-ne kaha maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya aap ke paas aur bhi kuchh aayatein ya soortein hain jo is Quran mein nahi hain (yani mashhoor musahaf mein) aur kabhi Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne yun kaha ke jo aam logon ke paas nahi hain. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha qism us Allah ki jisne daana cheer kar ugaayaa aur jaan ko paida kya hamarey paas us Quran ke siwa aur kuchh nahi hai. albatta aik samajh hai jo Allah Taala apni kitab ki jis ko chahta hai inayat farmata hai aur wo jo us waraq pe likha hua hai. abu-Juhaifa ne kaha us waraq pe kya likha hai? unhon-ne kaha diyat aur qaidi chhudaaney ke ehkaam aur ye masla ke musalman kaafir ke badley qatl na kya jaey."
6916,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' dekho aur paighambaron se mujh ko fazeelat mat do. ''
6917,"yahood mein se aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, usko kisi ne tamaancha lagaya tha. kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumharey ashaab mein se aik Ansari shakhs ne mujh ko tamaancha maara . aap ne logon se farmaya usko bulao to unhon-ne bulaya (wo hazir hua) aap ne puchha tu ney iske munh par tamaancha kyon maara . wo kehney laga : ya Rasulullah ! aisa hua ke main yahudiyon ke paas se guzra , maine suna ye Yahudi yun qism kha raha tha qism us parwardigar ki jisne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko sarey aadmiyon mein se chun liya. maine kaha kya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhi wo afzal hain? aur us waqt mujhey ghussa aa gaya. maine aik tamaancha laga diya ( ghussey mein ye khata mujh se ho gai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( dekho khayal rakho (aur paighambaron par mujh ko fazeelat na do qiyamat ke din aisa hoga sab log ( haibat khudawandi se) behosh ho jaeinge phir main sabse pahley hosh mein aaoonga . kya dekhunga Musa (Alaihissalam) ( mujh se bhi pahley) arsh ka aik kona thaamey khadey hain. ab ye main nahi janta ke wo mujh se pahley hosh mein aa jaeinge ya kohe-toor par jo (duniyaa mein) behosh ho chukey they iske badal wo aakhirat mein behosh hi na hongey."
